description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BARTS HEALTH LONDON NHS TRUST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Locum Consultant Respiratory Physician with a specialist interest in Cystic Fibrosis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;10 PA contract – for six months in the first instance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full-Time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are delighted to offer an opportunity for a highly motivated, ambitious individual to join our dynamic Respiratory Medicine service based at St Bartholomew’s Hospital, Barts Health NHS Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will join an experienced multidisciplinary team that provides care for adults with Cystic Fibrosis (CF) and manage patients with non-CF bronchiectasis and complex lung infections. The post is based at the St Bartholomew’s Hospital site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should be eligible for or have full GMC registration with a licence to practise and be on the Specialist Register for Respiratory Medicine or be within 3 months of obtaining this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameVeronica WhiteJob titleClinical Director, Respiratory MedicineEmail addressveronica.white6@nhs.netTelephone number0207 416 5000Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information regarding the opportunity, please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Danie Watson, Consultant Respiratory Physician, danie.watson@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Nadia Shafi, Consultant Respiratory Physician, n.shafi1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Veronica White, Clinical Director, Respiratory Medicine, veronica.white6@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A final shortlist will be ready approximately one week after the closing date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Veronica White, telephone 02074165000, email veronica.white6@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
